metadata.name: Take off
metadata.description:
The abstraction and sweep of the image takes away the restlessness of perfectionism, leaving me in a position of loss of control. 

Liftoff marks the beginning of my journey as a Crypto Artist on the Ethereum network with a smart contract of my own in Manifold.  

Lightpainting - Abstraction  
Experimental photography  
Dimensions 2432 x 1642
